<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-59-0305 </DOCNO><TEXT>A preventive maintenance approach used successfully by the airlines andthe military is reliability centred maintenance (RCM). Simply stated,RCM is a systematic consideration of system functions and the ways inwhich functions can fail, plus a priority-based consideration of safetyand economics that identifies applicable and effective preventive maintenancetasks. The application of RCM to nuclear plants is discussed.</TEXT></DOC>